<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/r-yukikaze" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5616326); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5616326&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180135" alt="R_Yukikaze" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5616326)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/r-yukikaze" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5616326); return false;">R_Yukikaze</a></span></p>
