<p><span id="u-credit-00033" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/short-stories:00033" target="_blank">编辑 &amp; 评论</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00033-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jane-rochester" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4291882); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4291882&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180136" alt="Jane Rochester" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4291882)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jane-rochester" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4291882); return false;">Jane Rochester</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1592995378 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">24 Jun 2020 10:42</span></p>
</div>
