<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/short-stories:00089/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>20██/██/██ ██:██, 地点：██████</p>
<hr />
<p>你一直深爱着她。<br />
虽然你已经忘记了她的面容和身姿，忘记了你们的相识与相爱，忘记了她同你度过的那些时光。<br />
但你依然不会忘记对<a href="/scp-3000">它</a>的爱。</p>
<hr />
